reviewText: This movie should have been called "The Rise and Death of MTV." It was a hodgepodge of video clips that had nothing to do with the title.

This is a rudimentary, appropriate documentary for older high school students in a music history, mass media, social studies or English course. It gives a basic overview of the history of the music video, just as it asserts. It is a good starting place for further research and deeper analysis.
Nothing insightful here. Looks like sonething made for broadcast.
Nothing insightful here. Looks like something made for tv.
